channel.title: Has anybody od you ever launched a binary options site?
channel.description:
Hello guys,
I am thinking to create a binary options site. The main reason for this is that I see a lot of demand for this within the space of cryptocurrencies.
Has anybody of you launched such a site or has some experience? What are the most important factors when considering such a project?
Appreciate your replies!
